table.name: product_detailed
table.viewSql: SELECT supplier_products.id AS supplier_product_id, supplier_products.sku, supplier_products.name AS product_name, supplier_products.status, supplier_products.min_qty, ''::text AS barcode, suppliers.id AS supplier_id, suppliers.name AS supplier_name, supplier_products.preference AS supplier_rank, supplier_products.supplier_sku, prices.warehouse_id, warehouse.name AS warehouse_name, prices.store_id, prices.store_global_id, prices.trade_cost, prices.trade_cost_units, prices.trade_cost_nanos, prices.start_date AS trade_cost_start_date, discounts.static_value AS off_invoice_static_value, discounts.static_value_units AS off_invoice_static_value_units, discounts.static_value_nanos AS off_invoice_static_value_nanos, discounts.percentile_value AS off_invoice_percentile_value, discounts.start_date AS discount_start_date, 0 AS vat_percentage FROM ((((supplier_products JOIN suppliers ON (((supplier_products.supplier_id = suppliers.id) AND ((suppliers.deleted_at IS NULL) OR (suppliers.deleted_at = '0001-01-01 00:00:00'::timestamp without time zone))))) JOIN prices ON (((supplier_products.id = prices.supplier_product_id) AND ((prices.deleted_at IS NULL) OR (prices.deleted_at = '0001-01-01 00:00:00'::timestamp without time zone))))) LEFT JOIN discounts ON (((prices.id = discounts.price_id) AND (discounts.discount_type = 'OFF_INVOICE'::discount_type) AND ((discounts.deleted_at IS NULL) OR (discounts.deleted_at = '0001-01-01 00:00:00'::timestamp without time zone))))) LEFT JOIN warehouse ON ((((prices.warehouse_id)::text = (warehouse.id)::text) AND ((warehouse.deleted_at IS NULL) OR (warehouse.deleted_at = '0001-01-01 00:00:00'::timestamp without time zone))))) WHERE ((supplier_products.deleted_at IS NULL) OR (supplier_products.deleted_at = '0001-01-01 00:00:00'::timestamp without time zone)) ORDER BY supplier_products.id, supplier_products.sku;
